---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Accessibility Statement" description="Accessibility statement for Valiant Vineyards website.">
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground sm:text-5xl">
          Accessibility Statement
        </h1>

        <div class="mt-12 space-y-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground">
          <p>
            Valiant Vineyards, Inc. is committed to ensuring that our website is accessible and usable for all visitors, including individuals with disabilities.
          </p>
          <p>
            We believe in providing a positive web experience for everyone and strive to follow accessibility best practices wherever feasible.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 space-y-10">
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground">
              Our Efforts Toward Accessibility
            </h2>
            <div class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground">
              <p>We take the following steps to improve and maintain our website's accessibility:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
                <li>Using clean, semantic HTML where possible</li>
                <li>Maintaining readable text sizes and clear visual hierarchy</li>
                <li>Adding alternative text ("alt text") to images when appropriate</li>
                <li>Using responsive design suitable for a wide range of devices</li>
                <li>Reviewing our website periodically to improve accessibility features</li>
              </ul>
              <p>While we work to adhere to commonly recognized accessibility standards, our efforts are ongoing.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground">
              Third-Party Content
            </h2>
            <div class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground">
              <p>
                Our website may include links to third-party content or services. We cannot guarantee the accessibility of content provided outside of our direct control.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground">
              Feedback and Assistance
            </h2>
            <div class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground">
              <p>We welcome your feedback on the accessibility of our website.</p>
              <p>
                If you experience any difficulty accessing content, need information in an alternative format, or have suggestions for improvement, please contact us:
              </p>
              <p>
                Email: <a href="mailto:wine@valiantvineyards.us" class="text-gold hover:underline">wine@valiantvineyards.us</a><br />
                Phone: <a href="tel:605-624-4500" class="text-gold hover:underline">605-624-4500</a><br />
                Address:<br />
                Valiant Vineyards, Inc.<br />
                1500 W Main St<br />
                Vermillion, SD 57069
              </p>
              <p>We will do our best to assist you.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground">
              Commitment to Improvement
            </h2>
            <div class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground">
              <p>
                We are continually working to refine and enhance the accessibility of our website and services. Your feedback helps us achieve that goal.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
